text.tspan: Estimated deaths from volcanic eruptions, World
estimated number of deaths from volcanic eruption events. This includes direct deaths from volcanic eruptions, in
addition to secondary impacts (such as a tsunami or earthquake triggered by an eruption). Due to data availability,
reporting and evidence, it's expected that recent data will be more complete than the long historical record.
Source: National Geophysical Data Center (NGDC) of the NOAA
